class App extends Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props);
    this.state = {
      columnDefs:[
        { headerName:'Barcode', field:'barcode', sortable:true,filter:true,resizable: true,checkboxSelection: true},
        { headerName:'Product Name', field:'name', sortable:true,filter:true,resizable: true},
        { headerName:'Price', field:'price', sortable:true,filter:true,resizable: true},
        { headerName:'Category', field:'category', sortable:true,filter:true,resizable: true},
        { headerName:'SubCategory', field:'subcategory', sortable:true,filter:true,resizable: true},
        { headerName:'Type', field:'type', sortable:true,filter:true,resizable: true},
        { headerName:'Brand', field:'brand', sortable:true,filter:true,resizable: true},
        { headerName:'Last Scan', field:'last_scan', sortable:true,filter:true,resizable: true},
      ],
      rowData:[
        // { name: 'Toyota', price: 1500, category:'Laban',brand:'Maraie'}
      ],
      selected:false
    };
  }


  componentDidMount() {
    this.arrange_data(data_to_arrange)
    // console.log(this.gridApi.getSelectedNodes());
  }



  arrange_data = async (data) => {
    console.log(data);
    let returned_data = []
    await data.map(item =>(
      returned_data.push({barcode:item.barcode,name:item.name,category:item.main_category,subcategory:item.sub_category,type:item.type,brand:item.brand,last_scan:item.last_scan_time,price:item.price.toFixed(2)})
    ))
    await this.setState({
      rowData:returned_data
    })
    console.log('done');
  }

  onButtonClick = () => {
    const selectedNodes = this.gridApi.getSelectedNodes()
    const selectedData = selectedNodes.map( node => node.data )
    const selectedDataStringPresentation = selectedData.map( node => node.barcode + ' ' + node.name).join(', ')
    alert(`Selected nodes: ${selectedDataStringPresentation}`)
    this.setState({selected:true})
  }

  render() {
    return (
        <div className="container">
          <div style={{marginTop: 10,marginBottom: 10,display: 'flex',flexDirection: 'row',justifyContent: 'space-between',alignItems: 'center',width: '100%'}}>
            <Button onClick={this.onButtonClick} variant="contained" color="primary">
              تعطيل المنتجات المختارة
            </Button>
            <Button onClick={this.onButtonClick} variant="contained" color="primary">
              تحديث المنتجات المختارة
            </Button>
            {/* <button onClick={this.onButtonClick} style={{borderWidth: 1,borderColor: '#6EB536',color:'white',marginBottom: 10,padding: 10,backgroundColor: '#6EB536',borderRadius: 8}}></button>
            <button onClick={this.onButtonClick} style={{borderWidth: 1,borderColor: '#6EB536',color:'white',marginBottom: 10,padding: 10,backgroundColor: '#6EB536',borderRadius: 8}}>تحديث تاريخ البيع</button> */}
          </div>
          <div
            className="ag-theme-balham"
            style={{
              width:'100%',
              height:800
            }}>
            <AgGridReact
              onGridReady={ params => this.gridApi = params.api }
              columnDefs={this.state.columnDefs}
              rowData={this.state.rowData}
              headerHeight={80}
              rowSelection="multiple"
            // sizeColumnsToFit={true}
            />
          </div>
          <div style={{display: 'flex',flexDirection: 'row',justifyContent: 'flex-end'}}>
            {/* <Fab color="primary" aria-label="add" >
              <AddIcon />
            </Fab> */}
            <Fab>

              <Action
                text="Email"
                onClick={handleEmailOnClick}
              />
              <Action
                  text="Help"
                  onClick={handleHelpOnClick}
                >
                <i className="fa fa-help" />
              </Action>

              <SomeCustomComponent
                text="Foobar!"
                onClick={handleTheFooBarOnClick}
              >
                  <i className="fa fa-foo-bar-fa-foo" />
                </SomeCustomComponent>
            </Fab>

          </div>

        </div>
    );
  }

}

export default App;
